00:03:07.590 --> 00:03:09.331
so this is gonna be equal to,

00:03:09.331 --> 00:03:10.585
well, rounded to the nearest integer,

00:03:10.585 --> 00:03:12.001
well, even to the nearest hundredth,

00:03:12.001 --> 00:03:14.207
this is gonna be equal to 10.

00:03:14.207 --> 00:03:16.726
So this is the length
of this side over here,

00:03:16.726 --> 00:03:18.967
